column5: any one heading up to the south sore for the walleye opener i am leaving tommorow am... last time i was up there for hardwater fishing was 5 yrs ago... wondering if anything has changed....thxs..scott
Where are you and how long you going for?  Been about the same amount of time for me since I was there last.
we are staying at the waltonian inn for sat,sun,monday night..hopefully it will be as good as 5 yrs ago opener..

The regs changed a few years ago. The slot is now in place for the winter. Don't know much about early season fish locations but I'm sure your hosts would do their best to put you over fish. Your ability to hook and then land them?
